Do something. Retry on failure for at most {@code numOfRetries} times.<br />\n */<br />\nvoid doSomething(int numOfRetries) {<br />\n　try {<br />\n　　......<br />\n　} catch (Exception e) {<br />\n　　if (numOfRetries &gt; 0) {<br />\n　　　doSomething( numOfRetries - 1 );<br />\n　　} else {<br />\n　　　throw e;<br />\n　　}<br />\n　}<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n// retry at most three times<br />\ndoSomethingWithRetry(3);</blockquote><br />\nretry pattern <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5a0e2e7cbd46888bd6332f23874f6eb744978e","tid":185244,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:07:05.000Z","msg":"[code]void foo(){<br />\n    try{<br />\n        // do something<br />\n    catch(Exception e){<br />\n        // do something<br />\n        foo();<br />\n    }<br />\n}<br />\n[/code]<br />\n咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37311c073091a071a95cb2009a827468cb265872","tid":185244,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"想係production debug？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253e2b4b5f502ff4fe8b820045ecdf79b66290d4","tid":185244,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"for (boolean canLoop = true; canLoop; ) {<br />\n　　try{<br />\n　　　　canLoop = false;<br />\n　　　　System.out.println(&quot;break&quot;);<br />\n　　} (Exception ex) {<br />\n　　　　System.out.println(&quot;loop&quot;);<br />\n　　}<br />\n}"}]}